name: 谢尔比·薛斯内斯
name_en: 谢尔比·薛斯内斯 Shelby Chesnes
name_full: 谢尔比·薛斯内斯 Shelby Chesnes
introduction: Lovely, buxom, and shapely 5'3" brunette knockout Shelby Chesnes was born on February 14, 1991 in Jupiter, Florida. Shelby when she was a little girl posed for her amateur photographer mother's experiments in light and composition. Moreover, Chesnes was a member of an all-star competitive cheerleading team in high school. Following graduation from high school, Shelby attended college so she could acquire an associate's degree and started her own spray tan business. After sending her portfolio to Playboy, Chesnes was selected to be Playboy's Playmate of the Month for July, 2012. An avid health and fitness nut, Shelby does yoga and Pilates in her spare time.
